Multicriteria Decision Analysis to Support Health Technology Assessment 
Agencies: Benefits, Limitations, and the Way Forward.

Baltussen R(1), Marsh K(2), Thokala P(3), Diaby V(4), Castro H(5), Cleemput 
I(6), Garau M(7), Iskrov G(8), Olyaeemanesh A(9), Mirelman A(10), Mobinizadeh 
