National Burden Estimates of healthy life lost in India, 2017: an analysis using 
direct mortality data and indirect disability data.

Menon GR(1), Singh L(2), Sharma P(2), Yadav P(2), Sharma S(2), Kalaskar S(2), 
Singh H(2), Adinarayanan S(2), Joshua V(2), Kulothungan V(2), Yadav J(2), Watson 
