69. Age Ageing. 2019 Dec 1;49(1):57-66. doi: 10.1093/ageing/afz125.

A modelling-based economic evaluation of primary-care-based fall-risk screening 
followed by fall-prevention intervention: a cohort-based Markov model stratified 
by older age groups.

Franklin M(1), Hunter RM(2).

